div.p:
—To maintain and strengthen US role in the Food
                    and Agriculture Organization (FAO), the
                    International Fund for Agricultural Development (IFAD), the World Food Program (WFP) and the World Food Council (WFC);

—Increase the representation of Americans in the secretariats and the use of
                    Americans as consultants in FAO and the other
                    Rome-based organizations;

—Play an appropriately active role in the World Conference on Agrarian Reform and
                    Rural Development and develop a policy on implementation of the resolutions of
                    the conference;
